'''SAIKAT''' (A '''BENGALI''' WORD)

    The meaning of the word 'SAIKAT' (a Bengali word) in bengali ''''KINAARA''''
 or 'TIR'(means bank/shore), it is popularly meant as ''''SEA SHORE''''
('''SAMUDRA SAIKAT''') or ''''SEA BEACH''''.
    In hindi the word ''''SAAHIL'''' exactly indicates the meaning
 of this Bengali word 'SAIKAT'.

  In Geography also the word 'SAIKAT' is used, provided the book 
is written in Bengali.

  You will find many Bengali guys with the name ''''SAIKAT''''.
  One of the famous Bengali singer is there,Mr. Saikat Maitro.
  One of the Mouth-Organ Player is there,Mr. Saikat Mukherjee.
  & many great personalities in the name of Saikat.

  There is a '''Bengali Association of San Diego, California''' in 
the name of ''''SAIKAT'''' ( '''http://www.saikat.org''' ).

  There is one more data available for 'SAIKAT',Great actress '''Sharmila
 Tagore''' acted in a Bengali film namely ''''Nirjan Saikate'''' in 1963 .

